OL,3,CDisability organisation has been saved
OL,4,Cdays before closure
OL,6,FShe said: "Our service is essential.
OL,7,FWhen we thought we were going to be
OL,8,Fclosing down, we were phoning clients
OL,9,Fand they were crying to us down the
OL,10,Fphone - it was very upsetting,
OL,11,Flistening to them crying.
OL,13,F"But now we've been able to phone all
OL,14,Fthe clients back and let them know the
OL,15,Fgood news. So our diaries are getting
OL,16,Ffull again."
OL,18,F"We even had our Christmas party early
OL,19,Fbecause we thought that was it, now we
OL,20,Fneed to organise another, this one
OL,21,Fwill be a celebration."
