OL,3,CDisability organisation has been saved
OL,4,Cdays before closure
OL,6,FMore than #60,000 has been given to
OL,7,Fthe association by local funders
OL,8,FSellafield, Cumberland Council and
OL,9,FCumbria Community Foundation.
OL,11,FClients, with organisation's support,
OL,12,Fhave claimed benefit entitlements of
OL,13,F#8.4m. Despite a lack of funding over
OL,14,Fthe last few months, their service has
OL,15,Fseen an increase of 43% from the
OL,16,Fprevious year to 1,908 users.
