OL,6,FExplaining how vital their support is,
OL,7,FMichelle added: "People from the older
OL,8,Fgeneration struggle to use the
OL,9,Fcomputers, they don't have emails.
OL,10,FEven with people not as old, we've
OL,11,Fbeen helping people open up universal
OL,12,Fcredit accounts because they cannot
OL,13,Fafford a computer.
OL,15,F"People also need to build trust and
OL,16,Ffeel confident in the person they are
OL,17,Fgiving their information to."
