OL,3,CDisability organisation has been saved
OL,4,Cdays before closure
OL,6,FThe charity - founded by people with
OL,7,Fimpairments - has been supporting
OL,8,Fpeople across Cumbria for nearly 50
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,FCentre manager Tracey Parker says they
OL,12,Fdid everything to keep the association
OL,13,Fafloat, including working for free in
OL,14,Fthe last two months.
OL,16,FShe said: "We worked on a voluntary
OL,17,Fbasis because there was no funding for
OL,18,Fsalaries. Thanks to this funding from
OL,19,FDecember, we will get paid again. But
OL,20,Fwe love the organisation.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/8
