OL,3,CDisability organisation has been saved
OL,4,Cdays before closure
OL,6,F"It means that much to us that we were
OL,7,Fmore than happy to carry on doing as
OL,8,Fmuch as we could to either see it
OL,9,Fwound up or to be able to continue."
OL,11,FTracey West, from Sellafield, said:
OL,12,F"We put #43,000 towards it to make
OL,13,Fsure the services carry on for the
OL,14,Fnext 12 months, but money's one thing.
OL,15,FThere's the other aspects around the
OL,16,Fresource of how we can support them to
OL,17,Fbe able to strengthen and become more
OL,18,Fresilient.
